2011 ica summer film festival bheja fry events at stanford 2011 ica summer film festival bheja fry facebook twitter email print add to calendar bheja fry india 2007 not rated 95 mins hindi with english subtitles ranjeet thadani lives a wealthy lifestyle in mumbai along with his wife sheetal who is a singer while he manages soundtrack industries at the request of his friend jagdish verma he decides to invite a singer and libran bharat bhushan to his residence for dinner as well as listen to him sing ranjeet suffering from back pain does not realize that bharat is also an income tax inspector and upon arrival at ranjeet's residence will virtually and hilariously turn his life upside down when thursday september 15 2011 7 00 pm approximate duration of 1.5 hour s where building 200 room 002 map audience faculty staff alumni friends general public students tags film other arts sponsor center for south asia division of international comparative & area studies contact smedirat stanford edu admission free and open to public permalink http events stanford edu events 283 28355 more info last modified august 30 2011
